  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8008637">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8008637/" class="title-link">攀登中国传统文化的阶梯</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8008637"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53672944/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53672944-20.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53672944/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">喵了个咪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-26"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-26 10:22:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8008637_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    国学是中国人的国粹，承载着中华五千年的文明，是我们民族，国家的精神支柱。随着传统文化价值观的破坏和逐步衰落，大多数的中国人都徘徊在精神和内心世界的十字路口。特别是在网络语言日渐发达的今天，人艰不拆、细思恐极、累觉不爱等等词汇，不断侵蚀我们的传统文化。习近...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8008637_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8008637_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










